### Supporting Bitcoin Development

This project is part of the broader Bitcoin ecosystem. We encourage users to support Bitcoin development through:

- Running a Bitcoin full node
- Contributing to Bitcoin open-source projects
- Educating others about Bitcoin and self-custody
- Donating to Bitcoin developers and projects

